    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ever wanted to try yourself as a contestant in a cooking show? Then your time has come!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Your Culinary Talent</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249770/extras/2474b118c2a63bec191b74de7add2093.poster.avif?t=1762803343\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249770/extras/2474b118c2a63bec191b74de7add2093.webm?t=1762803343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249770/extras/2474b118c2a63bec191b74de7add2093.mp4?t=1762803343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Like all other rogue-like deck-building games, every attempt to become the Greatest Chef will involve a careful selection of skill cards, a choice of activities, collecting special items, and of course, cooking tactics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is not your home kitchen. Every dish you are about to cook can deal irreparable damage to your self-confidence, knocking you out of the competition.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plan, decide and cook wisely to reach the final challenge fully prepared.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Tasty and Bold</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249770/extras/17d57d73450d41ae3923f3b3df3c166f.poster.avif?t=1762803343\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249770/extras/17d57d73450d41ae3923f3b3df3c166f.webm?t=1762803343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249770/extras/17d57d73450d41ae3923f3b3df3c166f.mp4?t=1762803343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All visual content is handcrafted with great love for the world of culinary arts.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Elimination Rounds</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249770/extras/801be4a93195a3c7389b0bb417eeba5a.poster.avif?t=1762803343\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249770/extras/801be4a93195a3c7389b0bb417eeba5a.webm?t=1762803343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249770/extras/801be4a93195a3c7389b0bb417eeba5a.mp4?t=1762803343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will face a cooking competition round at the end of each game week. A unique challenge awaits you in each elimination round. Prepare a dish that will impress the jury, and your victory will give you a bonus for the next week. Otherwise, you will be removed from the competition.</p>",
